description: This is a small application for sending notifications in 3 different channels. 1) SMS 2) push 3) e-mail. The application is built on a microservice architecture on the Spring Cloud stack, using components such as Gateway, Spring Eureka. As a send trigger, simply write to the log: 1) "sms was sent" 2) "push was sent"  3) "email was sent"
